videos.description: Trae Young finds an open Kevin Huerter with a slick pass and Huerter pulls up for an early 3-pointer.

videos.description: Trae Young welcomes rookie Cole Anthony to the league as he pulls up from beyond the arc and drains a 3-pointer.
